TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some informations.
Goodbye.
Charwood out in nowhere. Who keep it safe?
Text: 그을린숲 아무것도 없는 곳에 있어. 누가 안전 지켜?

TextEng: I seek the cult that prolonged the Neverwinter plague.
Text: 저는 네버윈터 역병을 연장시킨 사교를 찾고 있습니다.

TextEng: What can you tell me about Charwood?
Text: 그을린숲에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Have you heard of any trouble around here?
Me looks for plague-pushing cult. They hurt Neverwinter.
Text: 나 역병 퍼뜨린 사교 찾아. 걔들 네버윈터 해쳤어.

TextEng: You tells me abouts Charwood.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
Charwood seems pretty isolated. Who protects you?
Text: 그을린숲은 꽤 외딴 것 같은데. 누가 당신들을 보호하나요?

TextEng: Do you have shops? Merchants?
You gots equipments?
But you saw me not long ago.
What you talking about? You just see me earlier.
Text: 무슨 소리야? 조금 전에 나 봤잖아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Just formed? Port Llast is years old.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 막 만들어졌다고요? 라스트 항구는 수년 전부터 있었는데요.

TextEng: Where are your guards? Perhaps they know?
Text: 경비병들은 어디 있나요? 그들이 알지도 모르겠네요.

TextEng: You gots guards? Maybe they knows?
Who are the important people in town?
Who important around here?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Are you afraid of the Lords Jhareg?
Who Quint?
Who is Quint?
Tell me more about Charwood.
Me ask something else about town.
Where can I find the Mayor?
Where me find Mayor-guy?
Where's this castle?
Where this castle be?
Who's Karlat?
Who this Karlat-guy?
What does the gate guard protect you from?
What da gate-guard-guy protect you from?
